      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/how-the-global-carry-trade-impacts-the-selloff-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球套利交易的平仓有助于震动全球市场。彭博社的 Liz McCormick 在今天的“华尔街快讯”中解释了原因。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
